    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates and Bilstein B16 coilovers to sharpen turn-in response. Recently serviced with a valve adjustment and new rod bearings for preventative maintenance. It sits on staggered Style 67 wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. A well-sorted driver\u2019s machine ready for the apex.",
