    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2017 Lexus GS 350 F Sport, finished in a timeless Nebula Gray Pearl over a striking Rioja Red leather interior. This vehicle has been driven with care and serviced regularly to ensure it remains a reliable luxury performer. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though I want to be fully transparent: there are minor stone chips on the hood and a small area of curb rash on the rear passenger-side wheel. The interior is in excellent shape; the leather is supple with no cracks, and the cabin is strictly smoke-free. All technological features, including the 12.3-inch navigation display, Mark Levinson surround sound system, and the heated/ventilated F Sport seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine runs smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp shifts through all gears. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change, a new engine air filter, and a recent brake inspection confirming plenty of life left on the pads. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This car offers a perfect blend of reliability and sportiness for its next owner. Includes two key fobs and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
