    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven mechanical integrity. This meticulously maintained example offers a harmonious balance of performance and long-term value. Having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, it stands ready to deliver a refined driving experience for the discerning motorist who prioritizes both quality and sophistication.",
