    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks fantastic on the road? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved throughout the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a quality vehicle without that brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
