      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the powerband. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative handling characteristic of the M-platform. Significant preventative maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive top-end service. Finished with staggered alloy wheels and high-performance compound tires, this vehicle offers exceptional mechanical synchronization and a raw, analog feedback loop for the discerning driver.",
